{"tid":739280,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"建制勢否決查沙中綫","createTime":"2018-07-12T03:58:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-12T06:22:09.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"06ea7fff0408211821ca5416c13d3d4eed83bfaf","tid":739280,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T03:58:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180712/20447453\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180712%2F20447453&d=3l4Hg6ZQgzo2poxeTVxz%2B9tKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=ad228f18\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180712%2F20447453&h=698fb6af\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180712/20447453</a><br />\n<br />\n建制勢否決查沙中綫<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180712/large/1531329626_a4cb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180712%2Flarge%2F1531329626_a4cb.jpg&h=9b51c3d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n田北辰<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】民主黨林卓廷於本年度立法會最後一次大會，提出引用《權力及特權條例》要求港鐵向立法會披露中科、泛迅和禮頓就沙中綫工程質量問題提交港鐵的文件的議案。身兼立法會鐵路事宜小組委員會主席的建制派議員田北辰表明支持，但建制派人數佔優下，即使有田北辰支持議案仍很大機會在今日被否決。<br />\n<br />\n林卓廷發言時指，提出議案是因為港鐵隱瞞事實真相，承建商亦無公開交代，公眾無從得知有多少鋼筋被剪短。他批評在重要工程中何以沒紀錄，要靠前線人員憶述，又斥在港鐵在中科投訴禮頓時，竟安排禮頓律師在場，如同「big brother is watching you」，質疑沒有公允調查。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n田北辰支持用特權法<br />\n<br />\n運輸及房屋局副局長蘇偉文則反對議案，他指立法會由1985年設立特權法開始，少於10次成功通過，每次都有必要性而且性質嚴重，當中包括重大傷亡、經濟利益，以及公職人員利益衝突等，不認同要引用權力及特權條例調查，而且特首已指令成立獨立調查委員會。田北辰昨表示會支持林動議，認為可迫使中科、泛迅和禮頓能提供更確實證據，讓政府有更強理據鑿開紅磡站石屎檢查。他又批評有議員不支持有關議案是「縱容以後呢啲承建商全部打橫行囉！唔使理你㗎嘞，立法會，實有人保住㗎！」<br />\n<br />\n■記者陳嘉裕  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n屏風樓項目一波三折<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n佳寶五店肉檔遭潑漂白水　兩小時內發生疑涉豬肉價糾紛"},{"pid":"ef025ccdb863d9d103cf8c00b53fa32dc217f93b","tid":739280,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T04:01:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07ade5e8254a7f6ad193bcc6889ec1b0c1f606ee","tid":739280,"uid":141837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ef025ccdb863d9d103cf8c00b53fa32dc217f93b","tid":739280,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T04:01:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T04:02:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7089d2c26ff70d230e9350bbdcf0650372a368df","tid":739280,"uid":72457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T04:58:03.000Z","msg":"big brother is watching you"},{"pid":"06b10c10f29773c0fbb7daf7d71f4545dbaad142","tid":739280,"uid":6752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T06:22:09.000Z","msg":"官商勾結<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}